Package threepio.documenter

Interface Summary
Documenter Documenter is an interface defining the medthods and variables common to classes that convert objects and files to Doc objects.
 

Class Summary
Doc Doc is an abstract extension of Queue, that is versioned and removes case restrictions on contains(t) when t is a string.
XDoc The XDoc is a Doc that only accepts XTags and java Strings.
XDocumenter XDocumenter imports an XML file to an XDoc.
XTag A self-building class for a Tag from XML or HTML.
